Subject: Temporarily disable rtl-span reftest which fails with Pango 1.52.1

Ideally we would like to avoid a versioned build-dependency on
Pango 1.52.1 until that version has reached testing, so for now we
disable this test instead of updating its expected rendering to match
Pango 1.52.1 behaviour. When 1.52.1 reaches testing, we should reinstate
this (updating its expected rendering if necessary) and add a versioned
Build-Depends.

Bug: https://gitlab.gnome.org/GNOME/librsvg/-/issues/1063
Bug-Debian: https://bugs.debian.org/1065821
Forwarded: not-needed, Debian-specific workaround
